snippet.title: Why was Johnny Depp so Confused in his Relationship with Amber Heard? || Psychosis Explained
snippet.description:
https://www.goldcbt.com/  Why would Johnny Depp repeatedly say to news reporters & other people that he was so confused ??? An ongoing feeling of confusion in an adult relationship is a big red flag that you are dealing with the other person's psychosis, which is a common symptom of mental illness or unresolved past trauma.  Psychosis is common with people who are in the BPD, CPTSD, Narcissist & Psychopath personality disorder group.  In this video I briefly explain this phenomenon which is often misunderstood.  

#amberheard #bpd #cptsd #narcissist
